  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/ioconfigdirectory\/1811146-getindexentry\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T15:43:34Z\n---\n\n# getIndexEntry\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvirtual IOReturn getIndexEntry(\n intentry,\n UInt32 &value); \n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- **entry**: on return, set to the entry value\n- **value**: reference to variable to store the entry's value\n\n## Return Value\n\nkIOReturnSuccess if the index exists in the dictionary\n\n## Overview\n\nGets the entry at the specified index of the directory, as a raw UInt32.\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\n- **getIndexKey**\n- **getIndexType**\n- **getIndexValue**\n- **getKeySubdirectories**\n- **getKeyType**\n- **getKeyValue**\n- **getSubdirectories**\n- **update**\n\n",
